# Identity Mappings (Example)

> Example identity.local.md for a developer with three identities. Copy
> templates/identity.local.md.template to ~/.claude/rules/identity.local.md
> and adapt.

## Identities

### Identity 1: Work — Acme Corp

- Git name: `Jane Doe`
- Git email: `jane@acme.com`
- Path patterns:
  - `acme-corp/`
  - `Cowork/acme-`
  - `~/code/work/`

### Identity 2: Personal projects

- Git name: `Jane Doe`
- Git email: `jane@janedoe.dev`
- Path patterns:
  - `~/code/personal/`
  - `personal-site/`

### Identity 3: Open source

- Git name: `jdoe`
- Git email: `12345+jdoe@users.noreply.github.com`
- Path patterns:
  - `~/code/oss/`
  - `forks/`
